title: 2 BEDROOM - EAST SIDE COMMONS
posting_body: ['ABOUT EAST SIDE COMMONS', 'In 2011 TCHDC partnered with East Side Neighborhood Development Company (ESNDC) to redevelop three important properties on the East Side of St. Paul.', 'The G.A. Johnson Building, York Town Homes and Bradley Terrace Town Homes became the new East Side Commons.', 'East Side Commons includes efficiency, one, two, three, and four bedroom units.', 'The apartment building offers efficiency, one, and two bedrooms; the townhomes offer two, three, and four bedroom units.', 'Each unit was completely renovated in 2012.', 'The apartments have a controlled entry, on-site laundry facilities, high ceilings, original woodwork, off-street parking, and are convenient to metro transit.', 'The townhomes have central air conditioning, in-home washers and dryers, private patios spacious sites with playgrounds, either off-street parking or garages and a location convenient to metro transit.']
